<h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2 leading-tight">Roadmap to Being a Pro Scrabble Player</h1>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8 not-prose">Dictionary · English Solver</p>

      <div class="not-prose mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
