        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">Each tier builds on the previous one. Two-letter words enable <span class="text-white font-medium">parallel plays</span> which create hooks. Hooks create <span class="text-white font-medium">scoring opportunities</span> for high-value tiles. High-value tile fluency leads to <span class="text-white font-medium">bingo hunting</span> — the single biggest scoring edge a pro player has over casual players.</p>
      </div>

